Entries.default: An overfilled tankard sloshes in her hand.
"Don't watch Birta work, not unless you wanna lose your lunch."
"The food's okay so long as you don't look at it. Or smell it."
"Gotta get outta this pit 'fore I fall in."
"This pirate coughed in my face last week... now I don't feel so good."
"You start a fight in a The Hole, Birta'll make sure you see the bottom of it."
